originalText.text: We love living at 115, and the Rudin staff from management to porters are phenomenal. I've never experienced such responsive and attentive service and I've lived in NYC for 30+ years. If there's ever a maintenance question or concern, someone comes up to address it in literal minutes! Everyone is so friendly and also so sweet to my young son :) We're very happy residents!

originalText.text: It's only been some months for me to live in the building, but the staff provide a great and safe atmosphere and are very responsive. Having access to storage for bikes and suitcases is a big plus. The doormen are super friendly and approachable, making it easy for residents to feel home and part of the community.

originalText.text: It was very nice of the team (Ardit, Damien and Sharon) to host an afternoon tea event in our lobby. Making themselves available to be responsive to their tenant's needs and comments is very important. Who can't use a coffee break :)
